title: Luke asks: What if you crashed into a wormhole and went to the future? (Fur vs. Tech: Part 1)
description:
It’s the Incatible Hulk’s first mission with the Fur Force… only there’s no mission! I guess they’ll just have to jump in a rocket ship! 

Lessons include: Technology can be very useful as long as you use it responsibly; there’s so much more to this world than screens!
